Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.26,0:00:17.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.25,0:00:37.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這片朗朗晴空裡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.48,0:00:44.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將我們的心情 飛散灑滿其中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.99,0:00:49.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果命中註定的那個人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.13,0:00:52.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠是你那該有多好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.50,0:00:58.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是現實卻無法如願以償
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.00,0:01:04.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在閃耀光芒的風裡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.28,0:01:11.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢想的羽毛 飄然落下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.68,0:01:15.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鼓起勇氣邁向未來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.32,0:01:19.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 就這麼美麗地前進
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.83,0:01:27.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始奔騰的熱烈心跳
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.53,0:01:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躍動出跟那一天同樣的速度
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.77,0:01:40.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡你率直的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.75,0:01:47.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望能永遠看著你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.33,0:01:58.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第9話 大海與少女與夏姬的秘密\N是那些人做的對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.83,0:02:01.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第9話 大海與少女與夏姬的秘密\N竟然搗亂我安排的計畫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.37,0:02:04.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不覺得他們做得挺絕的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.07,0:02:06.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茜同學的情況
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.74,0:02:08.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很令人遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.11,0:02:11.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在還不知道實情的時候就…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.01,0:02:13.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好意外
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.88,0:02:16.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白妳居然會在乎這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.85,0:02:18.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想要怎麼做？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.92,0:02:21.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刻意不理會他們的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.19,0:02:22.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就是你們一番地嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.39,0:02:25.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然蝕之刻已經接近了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.62,0:02:26.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.82,0:02:29.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也該開始認真點了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.80,0:02:34.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期末考結束
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.63,0:02:37.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溫書假放完之後就會公布成績
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.87,0:02:39.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敬請期待～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.40,0:02:40.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掛了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.14,0:02:43.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和也同學一直請假耶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.01,0:02:47.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於那個啊\N我聽到奇怪的傳聞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.35,0:02:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說B班的日暮同學\N也一直曠課
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.88,0:02:51.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.88,0:02:53.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們兩個人啊…\N好像…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.15,0:02:54.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小茜？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.29,0:02:57.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人!好浪漫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.36,0:02:59.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別亂說這種無聊的八卦啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.69,0:03:00.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.73,0:03:02.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,楯，你什麼意思嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.33,0:03:03.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.03,0:03:05.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.23,0:03:09.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厲害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.47,0:03:12.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然私奔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.60,0:03:14.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好羨慕喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.71,0:03:17.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,私奔？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.08,0:03:19.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小茜她們？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.68,0:03:21.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是謠言就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.88,0:03:24.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說家裡那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.12,0:03:26.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像發生蠻多事情的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.72,0:03:28.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們兩個啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.22,0:03:31.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.42,0:03:32.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深優同學
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.93,0:03:39.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深優同學，妳跟艾莉莎認識呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.46,0:03:40.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.30,0:03:43.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我要負責照顧艾莉莎小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.77,0:03:44.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,午安
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.40,0:03:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是深優的同班同學
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.87,0:03:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,午安…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.11,0:03:53.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們有看到\N妳在創立祭的表演唷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.24,0:03:54.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很棒唷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.75,0:03:56.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.11,0:03:59.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭，真的好可愛唷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.52,0:04:01.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起，父親叫我們了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.09,0:04:03.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐，我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.42,0:04:05.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掰掰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.39,0:04:07.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真羨慕深優同學
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.09,0:04:11.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她那種表情\N在教室是看不到的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.63,0:04:13.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟是跟黃金天使在一起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.96,0:04:16.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,囊括了創立祭的全部獎項
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.57,0:04:18.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是很厲害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.20,0:04:19.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,創立祭…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.07,0:04:23.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.14,0:04:25.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的下定決心了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.64,0:04:27.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是託舞衣的福
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.28,0:04:28.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.28,0:04:29.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掰!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.28,0:04:31.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.92,0:04:36.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳又在想什麼了，舞衣同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.52,0:04:39.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個，我只是突然想到…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.86,0:04:44.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼一來\N私奔的可能性就提高了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.60,0:04:49.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我如果再跟她問清楚點\N應該會比較好吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.10,0:04:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我對這種事情也一竅不通
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.67,0:04:55.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼鴇羽舞衣同學
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.51,0:04:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問後夜祭上的這一幕
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.61,0:04:59.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳要怎麼解釋呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.38,0:05:09.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.39,0:05:10.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.45,0:05:11.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟黎人學長…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.39,0:05:13.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"黎人"學長耶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.52,0:05:15.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直接叫名字啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.53,0:05:18.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且這個叫法很巧妙～地
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.33,0:05:19.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夾雜了少女情懷在裡面
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.96,0:05:22.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這其中一定有問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.20,0:05:23.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪有什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.63,0:05:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以考慮考慮我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.14,0:05:29.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.54,0:05:31.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞衣妳…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.58,0:05:33.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少女情懷持續增強中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.91,0:05:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦!不是妳們想的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.78,0:05:38.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了，舞衣同學
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.78,0:05:39.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鎖定大人物!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.05,0:05:41.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目標是變成貴婦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.59,0:05:44.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個夏天就是關鍵啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.92,0:05:49.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊14號氣墊船的遊客
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.59,0:05:52.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再過去很危險喔\N請你們立刻回來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.30,0:05:57.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請各位遊客遵守規定\N快樂安全的遊玩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.10,0:06:02.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是暑假\N除了打工還是打工吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.01,0:06:09.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.18,0:06:14.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉呀呀呀…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.45,0:06:18.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞衣!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.32,0:06:20.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是晚餐!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.03,0:06:22.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洗一洗比較好\N新的魚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.53,0:06:24.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都不會抵抗嗎...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.33,0:06:26.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真是好大的一條魚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.10,0:06:30.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會長
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.27,0:06:33.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這模樣真的很MAN呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.97,0:06:36.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕的臉，這什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.64,0:06:38.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是東方鱸，小遙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.41,0:06:39.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,東方鱸？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.98,0:06:42.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿來煮火鍋\N或者弄生魚片都很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.28,0:06:44.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀呀呀，真是的\N（哎呀， 日語發音同東方鱸）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.85,0:06:49.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼？幹什麼啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.35,0:06:51.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不過是言語上的\N漏"東"而已嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.92,0:06:52.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是漏洞啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.79,0:06:55.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是遙同學
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.36,0:06:57.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞衣同學，妳好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.86,0:06:59.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦，姊姊？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.07,0:07:02.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞衣學姐～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.64,0:07:13.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為何會這樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.18,0:07:19.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,創立祭的慶功旅行呀…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.25,0:07:23.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞衣同學是來打工的？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.25,0:07:26.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我有急救執照
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.89,0:07:28.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就也帶著命…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.69,0:07:32.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行，讓我來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.70,0:07:35.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狡猾，人家也想幫姊姊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.33,0:07:37.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以起爭執喔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.34,0:07:43.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪之
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.41,0:07:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪～之～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.28,0:07:47.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小命，等會再聊了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.78,0:07:51.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小遙，什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.72,0:07:53.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫我擦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.79,0:07:56.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.79,0:07:58.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巧海
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.36,0:08:01.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有聽說你要來美星
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.49,0:08:02.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過沒想到會在海邊碰到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.86,0:08:05.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…還真沒想到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.87,0:08:09.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打工
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.07,0:08:11.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要加油喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.50,0:08:14.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也要多加注意唷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.75,0:08:24.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得不太像平常的你們耶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.25,0:08:27.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對楯的時候也是一樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.82,0:08:29.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會很害怕碰面的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.59,0:08:32.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被問起當時的事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.26,0:08:33.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以害我全身緊繃放不開
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.83,0:08:36.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是就算真要說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.79,0:08:39.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又沒辦法好好解釋…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.60,0:08:41.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以的話\N還是不要知道比較好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.50,0:08:44.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.97,0:08:46.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.71,0:08:49.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果妳很困擾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.61,0:08:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我也不多問
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.88,0:08:52.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.85,0:08:57.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有我可以幫得上忙的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.08,0:08:59.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請隨時跟我說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.22,0:09:01.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黎人學長…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.13,0:09:09.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥危險
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.90,0:09:17.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晶…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.04,0:09:19.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不游嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.14,0:09:21.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.27,0:09:23.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是要獻身於藝術
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.77,0:09:26.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來你不會游泳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.24,0:09:27.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那跟我一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.68,0:09:28.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.38,0:09:30.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不會游泳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.91,0:09:33.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該說…我沒游過泳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.15,0:09:35.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很小的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.85,0:09:38.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有差點溺水的經驗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.19,0:09:41.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過\N知道是因為生病之後就…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.76,0:09:48.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也畫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.17,0:09:49.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用來打發時間很不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.07,0:09:54.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你，晶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.58,0:10:06.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這風好大
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.42,0:10:10.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都沒看到，什麼都沒聽見
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.92,0:10:13.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的我只能想著劍道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.19,0:10:15.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泳衣的帶子掉了!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.53,0:10:23.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青春的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.83,0:10:24.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衝…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.84,0:10:25.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.09,0:10:47.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.73,0:10:52.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對，監視設備還沒壞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.60,0:10:53.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.50,0:10:56.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡已經沒剩什麼東西了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.93,0:10:59.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳為什麼要特地去那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.57,0:11:01.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不用知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.87,0:11:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不是沒線索了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.14,0:11:08.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰會想要來這個鬼地方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.59,0:11:18.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快，快停下來～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.29,0:11:19.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.62,0:11:21.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰考卷改半天改不完的？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.59,0:11:25.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會死啦～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.00,0:11:36.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎在創立祭上活躍的各位\N來到珠洲城家第25棟別墅
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.27,0:11:41.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然好像有不屬於這裡的人\N也來了的樣子啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.31,0:11:45.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外因為\N擔任監護人的老師們也在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.32,0:11:49.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以還請各位謹守本分\N不拘小節地享受今晚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.52,0:11:50.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.62,0:11:53.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小遙講話就是那個樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.12,0:11:56.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別在意\N我們真的也是局外人嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.66,0:11:57.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.03,0:12:00.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我的獵物，盡量吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.66,0:12:02.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪之也吃吧，這裡很好吃喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.30,0:12:05.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝，小命想吃什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.04,0:12:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那，我要那個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.27,0:12:10.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得是很意外的組合
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.54,0:12:13.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳閉嘴啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.45,0:12:17.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞～衣學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.32,0:12:20.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詩帆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.95,0:12:24.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看見了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.96,0:12:27.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞衣學姐其實跟神崎學長…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.46,0:12:29.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.19,0:12:32.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詩帆，妳怎麼可以亂說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.80,0:12:35.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油喔，我會支持妳的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.37,0:12:39.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為舞衣學姐說過\N要支持我和哥哥的，不是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.84,0:12:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這算是報恩喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.11,0:12:44.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這本來是秘密的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.21,0:12:47.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.11,0:12:49.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不能算不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.45,0:12:52.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是讓人感動到想哭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.08,0:12:54.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就叫多管閒事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.59,0:12:58.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,楯…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.99,0:13:01.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.37,0:13:12.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝不下了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.29,0:13:37.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.53,0:13:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你會在這裡!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.90,0:13:41.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是…因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.77,0:13:43.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比賽快到了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.63,0:13:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想重新鍛鍊心智…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.50,0:13:47.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就快給我消失!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.60,0:13:50.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玖…玖我妳又為什麼\N會在這個地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.41,0:13:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.68,0:13:53.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.15,0:13:56.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟你無關!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.28,0:13:58.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.38,0:14:00.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然有關!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.12,0:14:02.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…對妳…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.76,0:14:08.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.53,0:14:13.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有沒有怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.17,0:14:16.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還好…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.67,0:14:20.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起，打擾了!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.94,0:14:22.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.07,0:14:26.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.28,0:14:29.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.98,0:14:31.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個死變態!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.85,0:14:32.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.82,0:14:39.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣好嗎？放著他不管
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.46,0:14:43.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種傢伙，誰要理他!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.86,0:14:45.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我真的很訝異
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.83,0:14:48.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平常妳總是擺出一副\N不屑男人的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.73,0:14:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實際上…卻是這個樣子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.70,0:14:56.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開什麼玩笑!\N我可是有要事要做的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.47,0:14:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪有空談什麼戀愛啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.84,0:15:02.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像妳這樣簡簡單單真好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.21,0:15:05.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼，妳跟神崎吵架啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.85,0:15:08.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這樣啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.52,0:15:10.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等!\N為什麼妳會提到黎人學長？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.49,0:15:12.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是學校的大八卦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.63,0:15:21.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種就叫多管閒事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.53,0:15:25.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡，我到底在幹嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.78,0:15:33.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞衣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.05,0:15:36.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞衣？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.15,0:15:41.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞衣同學剛剛往沙灘那邊去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.89,0:15:42.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞衣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.03,0:15:51.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是護身符嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.66,0:15:54.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是兄長給我的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.66,0:15:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你對這個東西有印象嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.57,0:15:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有耶…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.67,0:16:02.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是我的兄長嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.41,0:16:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.01,0:16:06.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.08,0:16:09.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過如果像小命這樣的女孩\N當我妹妹，那就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.45,0:16:11.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.28,0:16:16.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擅自把出租用小船划出來…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.29,0:16:18.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是犯法的耶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.69,0:16:20.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有意見的話，就不要跟來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.92,0:16:25.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是因為這跟一番地有關\N所以我也想要知道嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.80,0:16:30.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳不是不想\N跟HiME的戰爭有所牽扯嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.17,0:16:33.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.84,0:16:37.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算假裝看不到\N仍然看得見啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.71,0:16:41.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玖我同學
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.48,0:16:42.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我夏姬就可以
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.45,0:16:44.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那妳也叫我舞衣就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.55,0:16:46.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏姬，妳是為什麼而戰？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.35,0:16:49.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.36,0:17:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳們太奸詐了!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.43,0:17:02.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然把我丟下，自己出來玩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.37,0:17:04.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.97,0:17:12.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是什麼地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.04,0:17:14.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一番地的分部
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.74,0:17:17.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是高次物質化能力研究設施之一
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.05,0:17:19.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.98,0:17:22.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡的監視裝置還有在運作
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.52,0:17:25.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要確實地跟著我的腳步
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.26,0:17:26.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.09,0:17:29.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞衣～快走吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.66,0:17:35.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算警報響了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.00,0:17:38.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些人要趕來這裡\N還是得要一段時間
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.44,0:17:42.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有發現文件，電腦資料\N光碟一類的東西就通知我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.67,0:17:43.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,10分鐘後撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.97,0:17:44.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.80,0:18:09.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏姬
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.03,0:18:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳自己一個人跑來接我喔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.57,0:18:15.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦，杜蘭也一起來了唷
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.05,0:18:24.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.79,0:18:36.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞衣，妳那邊呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.89,0:18:37.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有收穫
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.96,0:18:39.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像全都被破壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.53,0:18:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.57,0:18:42.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.63,0:18:43.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.63,0:18:46.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,違法侵入的現行犯\N我知道你們躲在裡面
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.60,0:18:47.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警察？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.07,0:18:52.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳想做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.91,0:18:54.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不能被抓到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.41,0:18:55.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.58,0:18:57.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對手是一番地
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.08,0:18:58.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳也看到了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.42,0:19:00.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且那些警察究竟是不是真的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.35,0:19:01.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.35,0:19:02.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是真的，那該怎麼辦啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.49,0:19:05.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點出來!快!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.82,0:19:06.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命，不行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.76,0:19:15.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那，妳想怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.03,0:19:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣做可就會有前科喔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.87,0:19:19.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之沉穩地…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.67,0:19:22.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳認為沉穩地處理\N能讓我們逃脫嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.11,0:19:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兜風耶!好高興!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.54,0:19:25.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.14,0:19:27.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.11,0:19:29.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.65,0:19:36.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.16,0:19:41.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我說好之前，先不要呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.07,0:19:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳也行行好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.54,0:19:56.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光是上次那件事\N就夠讓大家殺氣騰騰的了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.04,0:19:57.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次那件事？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.97,0:19:59.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這跟妳無關
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.74,0:20:02.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們只是普通的警察嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.65,0:20:07.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為上頭認為那裡\N只需這種程度的警衛應付
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.18,0:20:09.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過以防萬一\N在調查時多少還是緊張了一下呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.12,0:20:11.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迫水…老師？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.62,0:20:12.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.92,0:20:13.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.42,0:20:15.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爆炸頭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.19,0:20:20.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還必須去收拾殘局…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.87,0:20:23.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…選在這裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.97,0:20:27.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為視線不佳，最適合伏擊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.67,0:20:29.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死狸貓
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.95,0:20:39.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽，我好怕…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.02,0:20:41.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏姬，對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.95,0:20:44.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過妳不可以待在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.99,0:20:47.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,HiME有那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.26,0:20:54.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏姬？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.10,0:20:56.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毀掉一番地
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.73,0:20:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有跟這個有關計畫和打算\N全部都是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.64,0:21:01.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我戰鬥的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.54,0:21:05.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為此，我什麼事都敢做
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.51,0:21:11.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞衣…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.55,0:21:13.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我餓了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.22,0:21:19.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.69,0:21:20.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.76,0:21:22.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼回去？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.73,0:21:26.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的要這麼做嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.50,0:21:28.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是妳猜拳猜輸了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.93,0:21:30.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准有意見
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.70,0:21:31.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有車子過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.80,0:21:34.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行，要更撩人一點
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.00,0:21:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳這樣沒資格當女人啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.51,0:21:42.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我搭 ． 便 ． 車
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.95,0:21:47.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好耶!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.55,0:21:51.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玖我同學…妳…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.49,0:21:53.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹得好～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.36,0:21:56.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是出來…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.83,0:21:58.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找舞衣同學她們的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.83,0:22:01.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到看到好東西了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.70,0:22:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不～
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.31,0:22:14.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「請別迷惘」 這句話\N我說不出口
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.78,0:22:20.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有無法傳達給你的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.55,0:22:26.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太過寂寞的笑容搖擺不定
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.79,0:22:31.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撫過傷口 Lonely good-bye
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.03,0:22:38.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連熱情都會讓我痛楚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.54,0:22:42.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追尋著永恆的碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.57,0:22:50.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你曾是我的天空我的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.41,0:22:54.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將那段燃燒熔化的日子…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.92,0:23:00.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別忘記 要時時想起
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.93,0:23:07.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算只是收藏在心底
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.33,0:23:09.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Search for my life
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.17,0:23:12.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天還會再相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.50,0:23:20.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是喜歡你那清澈的雙眼 現在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.51,0:23:23.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走上各自的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.81,0:23:26.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重新開始前進
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.20,0:23:42.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛋糕大戰!!!!\N東方鱸的正確食用方式
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.70,0:23:44.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛋糕大戰!!!!\N首先從魚鰓部位用菜刀切入
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.87,0:23:45.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.54,0:23:48.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接著就切開剝離剝離切開切…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.71,0:23:49.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小遙!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.67,0:23:54.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事情至少還是等妳\N會做一點菜了之後再做嘛!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.45,0:00:00.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.80,0:24:01.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（風華學園史）
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.17,0:24:04.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（大約第2.5章的部分）
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.91,0:24:09.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（摘自 珠洲城 遙）\N（學生會長競選演說）
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.75,0:24:10.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.85,0:24:17.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儘管本校的校風開明開通\N且尊重學生的自治權
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.52,0:24:21.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少還是得遵守最基本的紀律
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.59,0:24:28.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像藤乃靜留同學以甜美的話語\N來獲得各位支持是很簡單的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.93,0:24:30.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.13,0:24:32.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所謂好心有好報
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.37,0:24:36.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會縱容各位\N會求公平而嚴格地對待各位
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.01,0:24:41.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以求創造出\N和平且井然有序的校園生活
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.15,0:24:46.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以有紀律且具自制性為特色\N如此這般的校園…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.45,0:24:50.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～這是多麼美麗的光景啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.62,0:24:51.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.36,0:24:56.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位還是可以提出反對的意見\N當然也有需要改進的空間
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.63,0:25:05.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者有若干人認為這樣不妥\N但是這絕對是有必要的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.54,0:25:10.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然校風自由\N我們自身就更應該嚴格地…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.41,0:25:11.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不這樣不行
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.64,0:25:15.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以更應該\N讓我珠洲城遙接管學生會
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.95,0:25:17.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓這間校園…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.63,0:25:29.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珠洲城遙落選後
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.66,0:25:32.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也因為這樣的幹勁\N而被招攬加入擔任執行部部長
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.66,0:25:37.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,且成立了留名千古（？）的\N珠洲城執行部


